    • PROP_ACTION

      public static final int PROP_ACTION
      This user property is used to trigger actions in the client application. The value of the property is found at UserInfo.userProps[UserInfoC.PROP_ACTION]. If the value contains the String PROP_ACTION_USER_SHOULD_CHANGE_PASSWORD the user should change the password . If the value contains the String PROP_ACTION_USER_MUST_CHANGE_PASSWORD, the user must change the password. If the value contains the String PROP_ACTION_END_PASSWORD_DATE, the password expires at the ISO date defined by the next 10 characters. E.g. "EX20120405" means that the password expires at April 5, 2012.
      See Also:
      UserInfo.userProps, Constant Field Values
